title: Project Zomboid Build 31
description: Project Zomboid is an open-ended zombie-infested sandbox. It asks one simple question  how will you die?In the towns of Muldraugh and West Point, survivors must loot houses, build defences and do their utmost to delay their inevitable death day by day.
